1. Football_Points -

	def football_points(wins, draws, losses)
	return wins*3 + draws*1 + losses*0
	end
	Test Passed: Value == 5
	Test Passed: Value == 20
	Test Passed: Value == 3
	Test Passed: Value == 7
	Test Passed: Value == 0


2. Sum of Polygon Angles - 

	def sum_polygon(n)
	return (n-2)*180
	end
